title: 2020 Supercopa de España Final
text:
The 2020 Supercopa de España Final decided the winner of the <a href="2019%E2%80%9320%20Supercopa%20de%20Espa%C3%B1a">2019–20 Supercopa de España</a>, the 36th edition of the annual Spanish <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="super%20cup">super cup</a> competition. The match was played on 12 January 2020 at <a href="King%20Abdullah%20Sports%20City">King Abdullah Sports City</a> in <a href="Jeddah">Jeddah</a>, Saudi Arabia. The final featured <a href="Madrid%20Derby">city rivals</a> <a href="Real%20Madrid%20CF">Real Madrid</a> and <a href="Atl%C3%A9tico%20Madrid">Atlético Madrid</a>.
Real Madrid won the match 4–1 on penalties, following a 0–0 draw after extra time, to win their 11th Supercopa title.
